<br />
<br />I put the <a href="http://www.rockbox.org/" class="postlink">Rockbox</a> firmware in to my 2nd gen iPod nano and it could play NSF at least. I didn't test other codecs but if this page <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.rockbox.org/wiki/SoundCodecs">http://www.rockbox.org/wiki/SoundCodecs</a><!-- m --> is any indication it should play MOD, SPC and a bunch of other format as well.</div>

